OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778670176
OL,3,CTwo arrested over arson attack at
OL,4,Cformer synagogue in east London
OL,6,FA man and woman have been arrested
OL,7,Ffollowing an arson attack at a former
OL,8,Fsynagogue in east London.
OL,10,FThe 45 year old man and 52 year old
OL,11,Fwoman were arrested on Sunday on
OL,12,Fsuspicion of conspiracy to commit
OL,13,Farson and have been taken into police
OL,14,Fcustody, the Metropolitan Police said.
OL,16,FIt follows an incident at a building
OL,17,Fin Whitechapel, in the early hours of
OL,18,FTuesday which the force said is being
OL,19,Finvestigated alongside a number of
OL,20,Fapparent attacks on Jewish sites in
OL,21,FLondon since late March.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
