FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778670176
OL,3,CTwo arrested over arson attack at
OL,4,Cformer synagogue in east London
OL,6,FCommander Helen Flanagan, head of
OL,7,FCounter Terrorism Policing London,
OL,8,Fwhich is leading the investigation,
OL,9,Fsaid:
OL,11,F"Today's arrests are a significant
OL,12,Fstep in our investigation into this
OL,13,Fattack and our inquiries are ongoing.
OL,15,F"Our aim continues to arrest and
OL,16,Fcharge all those responsible for the
OL,17,Farson attacks and other incidents
OL,18,Ftargeted at Jewish, Israeli and
OL,19,FIranian sites in recent weeks.
OL,26,@sD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778670176
OL,3,CTwo arrested over arson attack at
OL,4,Cformer synagogue in east London
OL,6,F"We will not tolerate these hateful
OL,7,Fattacks on communities."
OL,9,FThe Metropolitan Police said officers
OL,10,Fwere called in the early hours of the
OL,11,Fmorning by the London Fire Brigade to
OL,12,Freports of a fire at a former
OL,13,Fsynagogue.
OL,15,FMinor damage was caused to a set of
OL,16,Fgates and a lock at the front of the
OL,17,Fbuilding.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@XO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
