OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778670176
OL,3,CTwo arrested over arson attack at
OL,4,Cformer synagogue in east London
OL,6,FCCTV showed the fire had been started
OL,7,Fdeliberately minutes before, and
OL,8,Fcounter-terrorism police took over to
OL,9,Flead the investigation, the Met said.
OL,11,FCommander Helen Flanagan is urging
OL,12,Fpeople to speak to the police if they
OL,13,Fhave any concerns about someone
OL,14,Fbehaving suspiciously. She continued:
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778670176
OL,3,CTwo arrested over arson attack at
OL,4,Cformer synagogue in east London
OL,6,F"While counter-terrorism officers
OL,7,Fcontinue to work closely with
OL,8,FMetropolitan Police colleagues to
OL,9,Fprovide protective security advice and
OL,10,Fsupport to various organisations,
OL,11,Fcommunity venues and businesses,
OL,12,Feveryone can play their part to keep
OL,13,Fthemselves and their communities safe.
OL,15,F"If you have concerns about someone
OL,16,Fbehaving suspiciously, please report
OL,17,Fit to us.
OL,19,F"Your information could help us save
OL,20,Flives."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU{D@AOU|D@GO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/10
