CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778670176
OL,3,CTwo arrested over arson attack at
OL,4,Cformer synagogue in east London
OL,6,FThe former synagogue in Whitechapel
OL,7,Fwas due to be sold at auction earlier
OL,8,Fthis year, with a separate bid by a
OL,9,FMuslim group to buy the building and
OL,10,Fconvert it into a mosque and community
OL,11,Fcentre.
OL,13,FDetective Superintendent Oliver
OL,14,FRichter, who leads policing in Hackney
OL,15,Fand Tower Hamlets, said:
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778670176
OL,3,CTwo arrested over arson attack at
OL,4,Cformer synagogue in east London
OL,6,F"This attack happened at a synagogue
OL,7,Fin the process of being sold to a
OL,8,Flocal Somali Muslim organisation, and
OL,9,FI know that those of all faiths in the
OL,10,Flocal area have felt targeted and
OL,11,Ftogether condemn this horrendous act.
OL,13,F"Our work to engage with and reassure
OL,14,Fall communities affected by recent
OL,15,Fevents continues, and as always we
OL,16,Fwant to hear of any fears or concerns
OL,17,Fso we can address them.
OL,19,F"I want to reiterate that no hate
OL,20,Fcrime, no matter who it is against,
OL,21,Fwill be tolerated.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778670176
OL,3,CTwo arrested over arson attack at
OL,4,Cformer synagogue in east London
OL,6,F"It is completely unacceptable and has
OL,7,Fno place here."
OL,9,FThe Metropolitan Police announced on
OL,10,FWednesday a community protection team
OL,11,Fof 100 extra officers to help
OL,12,Fsafeguard the Jewish community.
OL,14,FIn its initial phase, the team will be
OL,15,F"primarily focused on protecting the
OL,16,FJewish community, which faces some of
OL,17,Fthe highest levels of hate crime
OL,18,Falongside significant terrorist and
OL,19,Fhostile state threats", the Met said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@OO]wD@AOU{D@VO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778670176
OL,3,CTwo arrested over arson attack at
OL,4,Cformer synagogue in east London
OL,6,FThey added it would bring together
OL,7,F"neighbourhood policing, specialist
OL,8,Fprotection and counter-terrorism
OL,9,Fcapabilities" to provide a "more
OL,10,Fvisible, intelligenceled and co-
OL,11,Fordinated presence focused on
OL,12,Fprotecting Jewish communities across
OL,13,FLondon".
OL,15,FFollowing an arson attack on Jewish
OL,16,Fcommunity ambulances in Golders Green
OL,17,Fin March, as well as a number of other
OL,18,Farson attacks and incidents, 33 people
OL,19,Fhave been arrested as part of various
OL,20,Fcounter-terrorism police
OL,21,Finvestigations, according to the Met.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@MO]qD@\OUuD@GO]
